 string that uniquely identifies the source in the style to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which it is added."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"identifier"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A URL to a TileJSON configuration file describing the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source’s contents and other metadata."}]}],"name":"configurationURL"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Return Value","type":"heading","anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An initialized raster tile source."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After initializing and configuring the source, add it to a map view’s style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"using the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The URL may be a full HTTP or HTTPS URL or canonical URL. The URL should","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"point to a JSON file that conforms to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TileJSON specification","type":"text"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If a Mapbox URL is specified, this source uses a tile size of 256. For all"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other tilesets, the default value is 512. (See the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize"},{"type":"text","text":" documentation for more information about tile"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes.) If you need to use a tile size other than